The paper deals with visualizing the response of a deep neural network to a specific input, specifically in the context of image classification. This suggests that the paper is likely to belong to the Computer Vision (cs.CV) sub-category. Additionally, the paper discusses the decision-making process of classifiers, which is a topic that falls under the sub-categories of Machine Learning (cs.LG), Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI), and Natural Language Processing (cs.CL). Finally, the paper also mentions the application of the method to medical images, which suggests that it could also belong to the Neural and Evolutionary Computing (cs.NE) sub-category.
